#: luci-app-diskman/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/diskman/partition.js:137
msgid ""
"Are you sure you want to delete partition %s? This action is irreversible "
"and data will be permanently lost!"
msgstr "确定要删除分区 %s 吗？此操作不可逆，数据将永久丢失！"

#: luci-app-diskman/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/diskman/overview.js:205
#: luci-app-diskman/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/diskman/partition.js:113
msgid ""
"Are you sure you want to eject disk %s? All mounted partitions on this disk "
"will be unmounted!"
msgstr "确定要弹出磁盘 %s 吗？该磁盘上所有已挂载的分区将被卸载！"

#: luci-app-diskman/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/diskman/overview.js:129
#: luci-app-diskman/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/diskman/partition.js:159
msgid ""
"Are you sure you want to force unmount %s? If the device is being read or "
"written to, unmounting may fail."
msgstr ""
"确定要强制卸载挂载点 %s 吗？如果该设备正被某些应用读写，卸载可能会失败。"

#: luci-app-diskman/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/diskman/partition.js:324
msgid ""
"Are you sure you want to format %s as %s? All existing data on this "
"partition will be erased!"
msgstr "确定要将 %s 格式化为 %s 吗？该分区上所有的现有数据将被抹除！"

#: luci-app-diskman/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/diskman/overview.js:229
msgid ""
"Are you sure you want to remove this BTRFS pool? This will unmount the pool "
"and clear signature data from member disks, resulting in data loss!"
msgstr ""
"确定要移除此 BTRFS 存储池吗？该操作将卸载该存储池并清除其成员磁盘的签名数据，"
"导致数据丢失！"

